Steps for setting up the system:
1. Clone this repository to local machine

2. Open up your IDE's terminal and type the following commands (assuming you have installed NodeJs):
  - cd frontend
  - npm i

3. Please add an .env file to the root directory. The follwoing variable should be added to your .env file:
  - REACT_APP_HOSTNAME: 'http://localhost:3003' --> NOTE: you can choose other port number 

4. After insalling all the dependencies and .env, run this command:
  - npm start
